{"tid":2486421,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳肇始：不希望僱主因為員工不打疫苗而解僱他們 取消免費派樽檢測不是懲罰市民","createTime":"2021-04-13T01:14:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T21:30:19.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":203,"uniUserReply":78,"replies":[{"pid":"c1bc594894173c593a811c9f28bdbe35bcd6949a","tid":2486421,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T01:14:23.000Z","msg":"餐飲及表列處所將能在特定條件下，逐步放寬營業限制。食物及衛生局長陳肇始在本台節目表示，多個政策局及政府部門，未來一星期將約見業界，敲定在「疫苗氣泡」下放寬營業限制的執行細節，包括因為各種原因，不適宜接種新型冠狀病毒疫苗的人士，進入處所時應如何出示相關證明等。她說希望逐步回復常態之餘，可避免措施「一刀切」，指措施的大前題是想提供誘因，讓市民透過接種疫苗，來保護自己、家人及社會，強調不希望有處所的僱主，因為員工不打疫苗而解僱他們。 <br />\n<br />\n陳肇始說，由創科局研發的「智方便」流動應用程式，可以記錄市民接種兩劑新冠疫苗的時間和牌子等，指政府已經解決電子針卡方面的問題；建議未下載程式的市民，應盡快下載。 <br />\n<br />\n至於政府有意取消免費派樽檢測的服務，陳肇始說，行政長官林鄭月娥只是提出會考慮，強調從公共衛生角度，檢測及追蹤工作一定會繼續做，包括強制檢測。她希望市民不要誤會，指取消派樽安排絕對不是懲罰市民，但指檢測只會令市民在當刻知道自己有無受感染，並不能提供保護力。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2386933\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2386933&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DMjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=dcb7a7f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2386933</a>"},{"pid":"a9e652d3511d643957eee9738bbabdebcbda6953","tid":2486421,"uid":47697,"like":158,"dislike":0,"score":158,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T01:14:51.000Z","msg":"我梗係知唔係懲罰，係逼害"},{"pid":"863da23d620e1cf4756ad47fbe43d78aaf133975","tid":2486421,"uid":51271,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T01:15:42.000Z","msg":"Fall吻興只得50%嘅保護力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"229fd53388df0e586a4bd5f595004317462e0633","tid":2486421,"uid":227628,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"863da23d620e1cf4756ad47fbe43d78aaf133975","tid":2486421,"uid":51271,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T01:15:42.000Z","msg":"Fall吻興只得50%嘅保護力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T01:16:35.000Z","msg":"Four Hong?我three hing 呀"},{"pid":"939c4d0d360ad819126028dc8e5f3f140631da07","tid":2486421,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T01:19:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f58b48042b6745a34b0b9735e30f22b67728cd74","tid":2486421,"uid":111253,"like":37,"dislike":0,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T01:20:11.000Z","msg":"根本共產腥港政府只係不斷製造問題, 然後射返個波俾市民, 極權就係咁痴撚線"},{"pid":"38a52879de0d9c01f3e60ccbbf03fe4483632219","tid":2486421,"uid":174767,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T01:20:43.000Z","msg":"不希望? 好負責WOR"},{"pid":"ddb4a4fec23826a209d98dcfe8db263b282cb2ce","tid":2486421,"uid":27432,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T01:22:03.000Z","msg":"但而家係迫緊WO<br />\n即係點呀<br />\n好撚亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16cb5024b5582191f8025c0d8d184caf32d2f7e3","tid":2486421,"uid":282626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T01:22:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>強調不希望有處所的僱主，因為員工不打疫苗而解僱他們</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"732626b87b72978f4f22b4fd545b7e5168cd3805","tid":2486421,"uid":44513,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T01:23:41.000Z","msg":"30歲以下點？<br />\n三高/有嚴重過敏史的點？<br />\n大肚的點？"},{"pid":"8c0cd44a01a97744d08cef9db4ad604b5014052c","tid":2486421,"uid":1900,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T01:24:31.000Z","msg":"屌你啦  不希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8eec0b516ade2c2c3750ba1d92e17ada1b00525d","tid":2486421,"u