提出會考慮，強調從公共衛生角度，檢測及追蹤工作一定會繼續做，包括強制檢測。她希望市民不要誤會，指取消派樽安排絕對不是懲罰市民，但指檢測只會令市民在當刻知道自己有無受感染，並不能提供保護力。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2386933\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2386933&d=2BCMh5porRb4XQq0U%2Bi1DMjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=dcb7a7f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2386933</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T02:16:48.000Z","msg":"電子針卡？我屌你老母全民監控"},{"pid":"e6aae662a284f3450b7993ec704dcd69445606d8","tid":2486421,"uid":322130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T02:16:56.000Z","msg":"根本就係打壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d280a632f0fdfc6cf594f27c5efad52668be095a","tid":2486421,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T02:17:33.000Z","msg":"玩撚鳩支那廢老同藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲啲放番支那狗嚟，一定又會爆過支那武漢肺炎"},{"pid":"62b28417072cc701bd761d635c5e9a81af880bfe","tid":2486421,"uid":340189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T02:18:11.000Z","msg":"On9"},{"pid":"b6459f5ee669d5da4f4a8524f23ebc1449bdd0c7","tid":2486421,"uid":270657,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a9e652d3511d643957eee9738bbabdebcbda6953","tid":2486421,"uid":47697,"like":158,"dislike":0,"score":158,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T01:14:51.000Z","msg":"我梗係知唔係懲罰，係逼害"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T02:18:56.000Z","msg":"重可能會整多班３０歲樓下飲食業員工冇得撈。"},{"pid":"dcd66525c9b833acc4e5c1311e3e30c8f85cf6aa","tid":2486421,"uid":198389,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b091621cbc0d3dc28e3e2427e538728130b75c2d","tid":2486421,"uid":293937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T01:48:03.000Z","msg":"預備緊5月要爆第6波"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T02:19:52.000Z","msg":"爆咪爆囉<br />\n未撚驚過<br />\n就係唔打吹咩<img src